
- edit /usr/share/mc/extfs/extfs.ini to add "u7za" after urar.

- edit /usr/share/mc/mc.ext to add :
=-=-=-=-=-= Cut -=-=-=-=-=-
regex/\.(7z|7Z)$
	View=%view{ascii} 7za l %f
	Open=%cd %p#u7za
=-=-=-=-=-= Cut -=-=-=-=-=-

This must be added before Manual pages Lines to prevent handle 7z archive
like man page

- copy u7za to /usr/share/mc/extfs

- launch mc to try ;)

